00:38:34.310 --> 00:38:37.060
So we're the Law Enforcement
Action Partnership.

00:38:37.060 --> 00:38:39.800
So anyone watching from
America, please support

00:38:39.800 --> 00:38:43.220
LEAP as much as you can.

00:38:43.220 --> 00:38:46.730
And in UK, it's much the same.

00:38:46.730 --> 00:38:50.910
So I'm going to see now from
JS if I've missed anything,

00:38:50.910 --> 00:38:52.473
or to sum up for us?

00:38:52.473 --> 00:38:56.632
JS RAFAELI: No, I think
