The policy's already there.

00:48:47.880 --> 00:48:50.300
I wouldn't have to change
any law whatsoever.

00:48:50.300 --> 00:48:55.080
You prescribe heroin liberally
to those people that need it.

00:48:55.080 --> 00:48:57.050
So you go back to
the British System.

