You do that, overnight, 80%
of the market for county lines

00:49:01.610 --> 00:49:03.620
drug dealing by
children exploited

00:49:03.620 --> 00:49:07.190
would disappear completely,
because that's mostly

00:49:07.190 --> 00:49:09.130
about heroin.

00:49:09.130 --> 00:49:12.560
The crime, the hard
core of those people

00:49:12.560 --> 00:49:15.170
who are having a problem
with heroin commit,

00:49:15.170 --> 00:49:16.970
disappears overnight.

00:49:16.970 --> 00:49:19.590
Shoplifting stops.

00:49:19.590 --> 00:49:20.670
It sounds easy.

00:49:20.670 --> 00:49:21.300
Well it is.

00:49:21.300 --> 00:49:22.950
It's in our history.

00:49:22.950 --> 00:49:23.900
It's there.

00:49:23.900 --> 00:49:25.860
OK, OK, it's a bigger
scale problem now.

00:49:25.860 --> 00:49:29.490
We're talking
200,000-plus people.

00:49:29.490 --> 00:49:32.400
But if you've got to start
taking care of people,

00:49:32.400 --> 00:49:38.520
not everybody would need to
keep on a heroin prescription.

00:49:38.520 --> 00:49:40.380
Many people would have
found the stability

00:49:40.380 --> 00:49:43.272
in their life to move on to
then another kind of treatment.

00:49:43.272 --> 00:49:44.730
But if you invest
in the treatment,

00:49:44.730 --> 00:49:49.760
even a fraction of what is spent
on law enforcement, a fraction,

00:49:49.760 --> 00:49:52.890
you would tackle the problem
that law enforcement cannot do.

00:49:52.890 --> 00:49:56.320
And taking care of people's
cheaper than treating them

00:49:56.320 --> 00:49:58.460
as criminals, significantly.

00:49:58.460 --> 00:49:59.860
So that's the
first thing I'd do.

00:49:59.860 --> 00:50:01.900
Then you can start breaking
all the other drugs

00:50:01.900 --> 00:50:05.560
into the individual regulatory
needs that those drugs have,

00:50:05.560 --> 00:50:07.990
because they do have
different regulatory needs.

00:50:07.990 --> 00:50:12.010
Cannabis, you have to decide
what strength product, what

00:50:12.010 --> 00:50:14.316
type of product can be
sold to whom and where,

00:50:14.316 --> 00:50:16.060
and where can it be used?

00:50:16.060 --> 00:50:17.740
It's much like alcohol, really.

00:50:17.740 --> 00:50:20.530
But we can do better than we
